### AI Knowledge Base - base vars
# 说明:
# 1. 路径按 `AiKnowledgeBaseExecutionApi` 的 Feign 定义组织，默认带 `/aiEngine` 前缀。
# 2. `workspaceId` / `kbId` 可直接在 `meta.ext` 中覆盖，便于本地切换百炼业务空间或指定知识库。
# 3. 首次导入知识库时可将 `kbId` 留空；导入成功后，把响应里的 `kbId` 回填到下面变量继续测删除/检索。

@apiPrefix = /aiEngine
@contentType = application/json;charset=UTF-8
@acceptJson = application/json

@workspaceId = ws-zi3sfdp4xf4wsb6v
@kbId = w05enpcxa4
@traceId = local-http-kb-001
@scene = manual-http-test
@docId1 = file_0661cff9804e40dbb2808dc41524957c_16686760
@docId2 = file_f2352fe41c7f44b89e1f65be7412c1db_16686760
@topK = 5

### 1) Upsert documents
POST {{host}}{{apiPrefix}}/api/v1/ai/execution/kb/upsert
Content-Type: {{contentType}}
Accept: {{acceptJson}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "kbId": "{{kbId}}",
  "documents": [
    {
      "documentId": "{{docId1}}",
      "content": "张三，男，28岁，来自上海，当前职位是高级数据分析师，擅长 Java、SQL 和 Python。",
      "source": "manual-http-test/profile-001.txt",
      "metadata": {
        "categoryId": "default",
        "parser": "DASHSCOPE_DOCMIND",
        "bizType": "employee-profile",
        "owner": "codex"
      }
    },
    {
      "documentId": "{{docId2}}",
      "content": "李四，女，31岁，来自杭州，当前职位是后端开发工程师，主要负责 Java 与 Spring Boot 服务。",
      "source": "manual-http-test/profile-002.txt",
      "metadata": {
        "categoryId": "default",
        "parser": "DASHSCOPE_DOCMIND",
        "bizType": "employee-profile",
        "owner": "codex"
      }
    }
  ],
  "meta": {
    "traceId": "{{traceId}}",
    "scene": "{{scene}}",
    "ext": {
      "workspaceId": "{{workspaceId}}",
      "kbName": "codex-http-kb-demo",
      "structureType": "unstructured",
      "sourceType": "DATA_CENTER_FILE",
      "sinkType": "BUILT_IN"
    }
  }
}

### 2) Search knowledge base
POST {{host}}{{apiPrefix}}/api/v1/ai/execution/kb/search
Content-Type: {{contentType}}
Accept: {{acceptJson}}

{
  "kbId": "{{kbId}}",
  "query": "谁擅长 boot 框架？",
  "topK": {{topK}},
  "meta": {
    "traceId": "{{traceId}}-search",
    "scene": "{{scene}}",
    "ext": {
      "workspaceId": "{{workspaceId}}"
    }
  }
}

### 3) Delete documents
POST {{host}}{{apiPrefix}}/api/v1/ai/execution/kb/delete
Content-Type: {{contentType}}
Accept: {{acceptJson}}

{
  "kbId": "{{kbId}}",
  "documentIds": [
    "{{docId1}}",
    "{{docId2}}"
  ],
  "meta": {
    "traceId": "{{traceId}}-delete",
    "scene": "{{scene}}",
    "ext": {
      "workspaceId": "{{workspaceId}}"
    }
  }
}
